author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
I'm on tour with The Darkness - but return to the studio later this week so Justin Hawkins Rides Again will be back with more episodes very soon.  To every one of my 600k subscribers - thank you for your support.  If you want to check out my own personal project "Dreams On Toast"  - my new album with The Darkness - you can find it here:
